high_descs: Turn around then head towards the door, turn right then head towards the white table.
Pick up the knife in front of the square plate.
Take one step right, then stand in front of the white cup
Place the knife inside the white cup.
Pick up the white cup with the knife in it from the table.
Turn left then head towards the door, turn right then face the black table.
Place the white cup next to the tomato on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a white cup with a knife inside it on the black table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the butter knife off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the white table again.
Put the butter knife in the white mug that is on the table.
Pick up the white mug with the butter knife in it.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left and take a step forward and turn around to face the white table.
Put the mug with the butter knife in it on the front right corner of the top of the black shelving unit to the left of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a white mug with a butter knife in it on top of a black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn to the left and then left again to find the white table.
Pick up the knife from in front of the plate on the white table.
Hold the knife and take a step to the right.
Place the knife in the cup, towards the middle of the table.
Pick up the cup from the table.
Hold the cup and move a few steps to the left.
Place the cup and knife on the small black table, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and knife to a table.
